Three Cities", which was shown at the recently concluded Venice
Film Festival, will be screened. This will be followed by a panel
discussion with senior representatives of three academic
institutions in New York -- Columbia University, Pratt Institute
and the City College -- which have been actively collaborating
with United Nations Center for Human Settlements since the
preparatory process of the Habitat II Conference.
</P>
<P>
