sectors.
</P>
<P>
Muluzi is expected to hold talks with his host, President Sam
Nujoma, and will visit Walvis Bay Harbor, about 450 kilometers
south-west of the Namibian capital, Windhoek.
</P>
<P>
Namibia and Malawi are both members of the Common Market for
Eastern and Southern Africa and the Southern African Development
Community.
</P>
<P>
The two regional groupings both aim for free trade among their
members by the year 2000. 
</P>
