the Tanzanian government's appeal to develop infrastructure in
the lake, as large as 68,000 square kilometers. The ministry is
making greater efforts to convince them to invest.
</P>
<P>
The director said that sound infrastructure would attract
interested businessmen to open up investments in the lake where
transport services were erratic due to inadequate vessels.
</P>
<P>
He hinted that the government was also interested in
establishing a Search and Rescue unit on Lake Victoria, where
over 700 passengers died after the ship of Mv Bukoba sank last
year. 
