<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, October 2 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria's High Commissioner to
South Africa Alhaji Shehu Malami has stressed the need for the
expansion of economic cooperation between the two countries as an
impetus of the warming up bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
