around 332 US dollars maybe the pressure might be just to the
upside on the Aussie," Aggar said.
</P>
<P>
Gold bullion in Sydney closed around 331.75 US dollars an
ounce.
</P>
<P>
Tonight, the Australian dollar was at 1.2929 marks, from 1.2852
marks in Sydney previously.
</P>
<P>
Against the Japanese yen, the local unit was at 88.74 yen, up
from 87.51 yen. 
