<HEADLINE> One Million Shanghai People Travel on National Day </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 3 (Xinhua) -- An estimated one million
Shanghai citizens traveled to tourist attractions out of the city
during the National Day on October 1.
</P>
